modName: Sylvanas Windrunner RaceMenu Preset - World of Warcraft
summary: RaceMenu Preset for Sylvanas Windrunner from World of Warcraft
descriptionHtml:
Adds Sylvanas Preset for RaceMenu. 
Race: Wood Elf

[u]Required mods:[/u]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows [/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25395/?]Lore Styles hair set 
[/url]
[u]Recommended mod:[/u]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?][u]CBBE [/u][/url]
Sylvanas Windrunner Armor and Weapon (Google it)
Note: The armor is for the 7B body, but i used it with CBBE. There may be some clipping with the hair at the back while wearing the cloak and hood.

Just install with NMM or copy the files to your Skyrim folder.
author: Shorsey
